-- Jordan’s Khatib Turns Down Syria Mission Offer, Dustour Says
-- B y   N a y l a   R a z z o u k
-- 2012-02-14T10:04:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-14/jordan-s-khatib-turns-down-syria-mission-offer-dustour-says.html
Jordan’s former Foreign Minister
Abdel Ilah al-Khatib said he has turned down a proposal to name
him as the Arab League envoy to  Syria ,  Ad-Dustour  reported.  Al-Khatib told the Amman-based newspaper that he didn’t
want to take the position proposed by Arab League Secretary-
General Nabil El-Arabi because the situation is not very clear.
He didn’t give further details, it reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
